Magic - Tumeken's Shadow=

Magic is a viable method for killing the Abyssal Sire if using a Tumeken’s shadow as the primary weapon. With the best possible gear, Tumeken's shadow can offer excellent damage output against the Abyssal Sire, comparable to the best possible gear with melee. Important to keep in mind is the overall lower defence of a magic setup, so you should be careful with keeping your health up. The method is low effort as it reduces the amount of swaps; allowing you to bring more supplies. 

The Eldritch nightmare staff and Accursed sceptre can be used interchangeably. It is recommended to use the Accursed sceptre for faster kills as it reduces the boss's magic and defence levels regardless of hit.

